---
title: Harissa-Spiced Chicken with Chickpea Mash and Parsley-Lemon Crema
description: We've dressed up chicken with a cape of this delicious paste – and what a superhero dinner it creates! Mashing chickpeas with zesty lemon and fresh parsley, then topping it with cool lemon crema, this appetizing meal is a winner all the way through to the final bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/harissa-spiced-chicken-ee11a491.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/harissa-spiced-chicken-58c9506b3bddb556b230e3a2-fcd6488f.pdf
